summary: Adds a nice little dog in each player home! Nothing major, just a nice little environmental touch!
descriptionHtml: This is my first mod, but I hope to make many more, and update this one. It adds a dog into each player home, but hopefully in the future I can add cats, birds, dragons, etc. Enjoy, and don\'t forget to add some feedback! I\'d love to help you! :D
author: Overoxide
